OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773249077
OL,3,CFunding secured for multi-million
OL,4,Cpound wind farm in Dumfries and
OL,5,CGalloway
OL,7,FFunding worth #62 million has been
OL,8,Fsecured for the development of the
OL,9,FBenbrack Onshore Wind Farm in Dumfries
OL,10,Fand Galloway.
OL,12,FRed Rock Renewables began construction
OL,13,Fof the site, located north of
OL,14,FCarsphairn, in October 2022 with the
OL,15,Fproject now nearing commercial
OL,16,Foperations.
OL,18,FThe company say that the three lenders
OL,19,Fhave "provided equal project
OL,20,Ffinancing."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
