OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773249077
OL,3,CFunding secured for multi-million
OL,4,Cpound wind farm in Dumfries and
OL,5,CGalloway
OL,7,FIn a statement Shi Weifei, Red Rock's
OL,8,FChief Finance Officer, said: "To self-
OL,9,Ffund construction during particularly
OL,10,Fchallenging market conditions within
OL,11,Fthe renewables sector took a giant
OL,12,Fleap of faith, so we are delighted to
OL,13,Fhave our turbines operational and now
OL,14,Fthe security of reaching financial
OL,15,Fclose."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
